    <item>
      <title>印度官员将 Byju 的贷方从债权人小组中除名</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/byju-s-lenders-kicked-off-creditor-panel-by-india-court-official</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度法院指定的仲裁员将 Byju’s 的美国债权人从有影响力的债权人委员会中剔除，这对于陷入困境、寻求避免破产的在线教育公司来说是一个潜在的福音。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/byju-s-lenders-kicked-off-creditor-panel-by-india-court-official</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 21:57:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克的 Starlink 计划让步，同意在巴西阻止 X 项目</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/musk-s-starlink-backs-down-vows-to-comply-and-block-x-in-brazil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克的卫星互联网提供商 Starlink 改变了方针，表示将遵守巴西最高法院的命令，阻止拉丁美洲最大的国家访问这位亿万富翁的社交网络 X。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/musk-s-starlink-backs-down-vows-to-comply-and-block-x-in-brazil</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 21:33:27 GMT</pubDate>
